The paper discusses the development of a cryptographic algorithm, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The algorithm also involves key generation and management, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). The paper also mentions the use of MySQL DBMS, which falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB). The implementation of the algorithm using PHP suggests that it may also fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper discusses the conservation of storage space and processing power, which is related to cyber-physical systems (cs.CY).
